Enum Constant Detail

ALL_PATHS

public static final AdmissiblePathModel ALL_PATHS
For each demand, all paths satisfying the hop limits can be used. Any explicit list of admissible paths is ignored.

EXPLICIT_LIST

public static final AdmissiblePathModel EXPLICIT_LIST
For each demand, an explicit list of admissible paths must be specified. Only these paths are admissible (provided that they satisfy the hop limits).
